  "description": "<i>League Football</i> is a football manager game where you have to guide a team from Division 4 to win the Division 1 title as well as other cups as well. You have various options at your disposal to help you in your quest for success and these include player and formation selection, coaching, and buying and selling players. When your happy with your selections then it's onto the match highlights. You start with a screen with text with a clock counting upwards to 90 minutes. If there is a goalmouth incident then the screen switches to an animation viewed from above showing the goal area. If the chance is missed or scored then the game goes back to the text screen. You are able to change your players during the highlights.",
